{{Wireless embedded system |brand=Yunlink |model=HWAP80 |revision=-P48 |fcc_date=03/21/2018 |is_manuf=No |type=outdoor access point |fcc_id=2ADUG-P48 |pwr_poe=at |cpu1_brand=Qualcomm Atheros |cpu1_model=QCA9563 |cpu1_cspeed=750 |fla1=16 |ram1=128 |wi1_chip1_brand=Qualcomm Atheros |wi1_chip1_model=QCA9563 |wi1_802dot11_protocols=bgn |wi1_txchains=2 |wi1_rxchains=2 |wi1_sstreams=2 |wi2_802dot11_protocols=an+ac |wi2_txchains=2 |wi2_rxchains=2 |wi2_sstreams=2 |lan_speed=1G |lan_ports=1 |802dot11_protocols=abgn+ac |default_ssid=WirelessAP-2G-XX, WirelessAP-5G-XX |default_ip=192.168.188.253 |default_user=Admin |default_pass=admin |oui=78:D3:8D |oui_eth=78:D3:8D }} Also known as HW-AP80.
